title: Great Barrier Reef [Old Version]
description: The world's largest marine community comes alive on your computer with this incredible 3D screen saver.  Dive in and experience it today! Features include: More than 25 authentic fish species, Dozens of different marine life, Two types of sharks, Listen to soothing ocean sounds or add your own music, Interact and feed the fish, Watch certain fish protect their territory, compatible with regular and widescreen monitors. The real Great Barrier Reef is in danager due to overfishing, climate changes and declining water quality.  We are committed to help preserving this incredible marine community.  A portion of the proceeds from this product will go to organizations who help preserve the reef.
